
## API v1
GET    /status                               Onetime::App::API#status
GET    /authcheck                            Onetime::App::API#authcheck

POST   /share                                Onetime::App::API#share
POST   /generate                             Onetime::App::API#generate

POST   /create                               Onetime::App::API#create

POST   /secret/:key                          Onetime::App::API#show_secret

GET    /private/recent                       Onetime::App::API#show_metadata_recent
GET    /metadata/recent                      Onetime::App::API#show_metadata_recent

GET    /private/:key                         Onetime::App::API#show_metadata
POST   /private/:key                         Onetime::App::API#show_metadata
GET    /metadata/:key                        Onetime::App::API#show_metadata
POST   /metadata/:key                        Onetime::App::API#show_metadata

POST   /private/:key/burn                    Onetime::App::API#burn_secret
